channel.title: My RSPS help?
channel.description: Okay, so i made a rsps and i have been trying to put it on the internet for my friends to play. I know your supposed to make the ip in the client that you use to be set to 127.0.0.1, and the one u give out to your no-ip.org ip. but what ip do i make the source to be?
